1. “The just wrath of the Creator did once submerge the sinful world beneath an avenging rain of waters, Noe being safe in the Ark3 finally, however, the wondrous power of love purified the world with Blood.'' 2. “Watered by such salubrious rain, the happy earth which formerly abounded with thorns, now buds forth fiowers3 and (the bitterness of) wormwood hath been changed into the sweetness of nectar.''
